# Copy to .env.local (already gitignored via *.local) and fill in the real
# value. Get it by running `npx dexie-cloud create` in this directory, which
# creates a free Dexie Cloud database and writes dexie-cloud.json — use its
# "dbUrl" field here. Leave unset to run fully local-only (no login option
# shown, no code touches the network) — see src/db/cloud.ts.
VITE_DEXIE_CLOUD_URL=
